public class DefaultGemfireEntityInformation<T,ID> extends org.springframework.data.repository.core.support.PersistentEntityInformation<T,ID> implements GemfireEntityInformation<T,ID>
Implementation of GemfireEntityInformation and Spring Data's PersistentEntityInformation that returns the Region name associated with the PersistentEntity.
